Package: hdf5MEA
Title: R I/O Toolkit for Multi-well HDF5 MEA Files (BRW/BXR v4)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Hyojung", family = "Yoon", email = "hyojungyoon90@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut","cre"))
)
Description: Read and inspect 3Brain-style BRW/BXR v4 HDF5 files in R.
    Provides metadata access, partial channel/interval reads, plate/well layout handling,
    and export to CSV/Parquet/HDF5 for downstream analysis.
